              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37914541/" class="">第13页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rollingge/" class=" " title="如林">如林</a>
                (林无静树 川无停流)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37914541">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">随着理性设计者的不断胜利，生殖乐趣开始从帝国核心区消失。神话民族的人口洪峰从帝国边区阑入，淹没了末人的成熟文明。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-06-05 16:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
